Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.38,0:22:43.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&HBD7AA1&}敞开教科书的文字上
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.21,0:22:46.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&HBD7AA1&}字里行间仿佛随心起舞
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.42,0:22:49.89,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&HA82DE4&}踏着步伐走进梦境
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.89,0:22:53.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&HA82DE4&}一跃而起
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.22,0:22:58.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&HC593AF&\pos(150,1000)}未来并非早已注定
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.39,0:23:00.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1150,1000)\3c&H1C86E5&}璀璨的祈愿
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.15,0:23:01.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1150,1000)\3c&H1C86E5&}不论何种希望
